{"id": 2580, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今关于“约会”这件事，你都有过哪些顾虑？", "description": "最大的顾虑大概还是，没有可以约会的人吧。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 2653, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181024132315mdyfVSaDOEp6siLH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 307456, "content": "对方说，我请你吃饭。最后，追求不成功。让退还饭钱。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485592}, {"id": 307458, "content": "约pao不会有这种问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323352}, {"id": 307459, "content": "犹如配种站的两位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352500}, {"id": 311300, "content": "每次出门看自己长这么丑还有人要，我都心疼女友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182031}, {"id": 307461, "content": "到底要不要吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450211}, {"id": 307462, "content": "缺少聊天的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482344}, {"id": 307463, "content": "不喜欢“约会”这种表达方式 跟某人单独出去不代表跟某人建立正式关系 往往还是考察暧昧期 甚至只是从“认识的人”到“熟悉的人”之间过渡阶段 比较喜欢“go out with sb ”这种大家都没什么心理负担的表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651076}, {"id": 307719, "content": "怕相处过后发现对方不是想象的那样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164756}, {"id": 307464, "content": "怕自己胖胖的", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422595}, {"id": 307465, "content": "赴约的时候，老觉得心里面有个疙瘩，好像单身也不错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484593}, {"id": 307722, "content": "最怕突然离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282925}, {"id": 307467, "content": "他把我当备胎 我把他当真爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473131}, {"id": 307469, "content": "各位吃完饭就'渐行渐远渐无书'的各位相亲对象，麻烦把我的微信号分享给你身边需要的人好嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417174}, {"id": 307470, "content": "气氛万一冷场了多尬啊……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 411759}, {"id": 307471, "content": "真诚比较重要吧，我收银的时候我对女生抢着买单的行为特别的感动，爱是相互的对吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481201}, {"id": 307472, "content": "怕对方太认真，又怕对方不认真…", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436283}, {"id": 307986, "content": "表面笑嘻嘻，内心mmp", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488500}, {"id": 307475, "content": "尽量放松自己，其实他/她和你一样紧张。能让他/她放松下来，约会就算成功了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088231}, {"id": 307476, "content": "临了，怂了，硬找个借口爽约", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001049}, {"id": 308244, "content": "没有可以约会的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490039}, {"id": 307733, "content": "吃个饭，散个步就算发展男女关系了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146993}, {"id": 307479, "content": "没人约", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441773}, {"id": 334872, "content": "伪命题，跳过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 307483, "content": "约会？ 好久没体验过了…总觉得没有了以往对于爱情的冲动，也不清楚自己到底喜欢哪种女生，对哪种女生会有心动的感觉…其实一个人也挺好…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485679}, {"id": 306204, "content": "有心仪的对象，不敢主动约对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 224, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 306205, "content": "觉得约会是“大件事”，不想轻易答应", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 307485, "content": "设计什么让你想不开要约会的？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429934}, {"id": 306206, "content": "害怕场面尴尬，干脆拒绝约会", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 307486, "content": "总是会不自觉的去试探自己在对方心里的位置", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485689}, {"id": 306207, "content": "不想奔着结婚去约会，又怕被当成“没诚意”", "image": null, "praise_count": 190, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 307487, "content": "担心三观不同 好尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396825}, {"id": 308255, "content": "约会是啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488335}, {"id": 306208, "content": "想多约会几个人，怕被说成“找备胎”", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 307488, "content": "只会吃饭看电影，想不出别的事情了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444564}, {"id": 307490, "content": "约会不知道干什么，好玩的也不觉得有多好玩了，我的少女心不知道哪里去了", "image": "img/option/option/201810291746264cXwo8vIL70fWaPz.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485705}, {"id": 307492, "content": "最大的顾虑就是没有合适的约会对象哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20181029174747ozfglIrXKT6Ny7Me.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485705}, {"id": 307497, "content": "吃完饭，女生等着男生付钱这样真的好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054396}, {"id": 307498, "content": "约会，哈哈哈哈不存在的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485708}, {"id": 315691, "content": "他知道我抽烟会怎么想\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}, {"id": 307500, "content": "都是无收入人群，到底该不该AA", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028920}, {"id": 307501, "content": "只要男生一天生不出孩子，男女就不可能平等的 哼哼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 278222}, {"id": 307503, "content": "无话可说😶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395205}, {"id": 307759, "content": "IT直男：钱多话少死的早", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485566}, {"id": 307504, "content": "单身贵族！！！\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485733}, {"id": 307505, "content": "我想和你走遍我们想要去的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485734}, {"id": 307506, "content": "吃饭看电影都干过了，接下来还能干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728273}, {"id": 307507, "content": "尬聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670012}, {"id": 308019, "content": "找不到合适的衣服穿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 673866}, {"id": 307508, "content": "单身久了，不敢去约。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485750}, {"id": 307764, "content": "为什么每次约我的男人。满足的都想上床。谁能告诉我什么时候才合适上床。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486493}]}